title: HOUR 2 - Petty Oklahoma Fans, Greg Cosell

description:
Senior Producer/NFL Analyst Greg Cosell joins Colin Cowherd to discuss the NFL and the playoff push. Colin also talks about Oklahoma fans and how petty they are over how USC HC Lincoln Riley left.
